OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FWords by Sophia Ankel
OL,8,FA long-awaited from the public inquiry
OL,9,Finto what has been considered the
OL,10,F"biggest treatment disaster in NHS
OL,11,Fhistory" was published on Monday.
OL,13,FThe seven-volume report outlines what
OL,14,Fit described as a "catalogue of
OL,15,Ffailures that could largely have been
OL,16,Favoided and should have been."
OL,18,FThe scandal Hepatitis C and HIV after
OL,19,Fbeing treated with contaminated blood
OL,20,Fproducts during the 1970s and 1980s.
