OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FHowever, the report did name
OL,7,Fresponsible bodies involved, and
OL,8,Foutlined how they failed to prevent
OL,9,Fthe disaster from unfolding.
OL,11,FITV News breaks down these missed
OL,12,Fopportunities.
OL,14,F1. Knowledge of risk of infection from
OL,15,Fblood and blood products
OL,17,FThe risks of blood and blood products
OL,18,Fcausing severe infection were "known
OL,19,Fwell before most patients were
OL,20,Ftreated," the report found.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/14
