OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FDespite this, no steps were taken by
OL,7,Fthe department to ensure that the
OL,8,Fserious nature of these conditions was
OL,9,Funderstood by doctors, patients,
OL,10,Frepresentative bodies, or the public.
OL,12,F2. Failure to achieve self-sufficiency
OL,13,Fin blood products and stop imports
OL,15,FDespite recommendations from the World
OL,16,FHealth Organisation (WHO) and attempts
OL,17,Fby the government, the UK "failed to
OL,18,Fachieve self-sufficiency in blood
OL,19,Fproducts," the report found.
