OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FAdditionally, the "testing of blood
OL,7,Fdonated in the UK was not introduced
OL,8,Fas quickly as it could have been, and
OL,9,Fsurrogate screening methods, which
OL,10,Fcould have been used before those
OL,11,Ftests were available, were not
OL,12,Fadopted," it added.
OL,14,F5. A 'doctors know best' mentality
OL,16,FDoctors treated patients despite the
OL,17,Fknown risks of viral transmission and
OL,18,Fwithout informing them of those risks,
OL,19,Fthe report also found.
