OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FThey gave false reassurance to
OL,7,Fpatients, and failed to adjust their
OL,8,Ftreatment regimes to make them safer
OL,9,Fwhen such adjustments were possible,
OL,10,Fit added.
OL,12,FIn some cases, patients were tested
OL,13,Fwithout their knowledge or consent and
OL,14,Fnot informed of the result, sometimes
OL,15,Ffor years.
OL,17,F6. Cover-up culture
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/14
