OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FThe NHS' and ministers' refusal to own
OL,7,Fup to their failings "served to
OL,8,Fcompound people's suffering,"
OL,9,Fresulting in a decades-long battle for
OL,10,Fthe truth, the report found.
OL,12,FIt took until 2018 for a UK-wide
OL,13,Fpublic inquiry to be established, and
OL,14,Fup until then successive government
OL,15,Fclaimed that there was no wrongdoing.
