OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FMinisters "cruelly" repeated the line
OL,7,Ffrom Margaret Thatcher in 1989 that
OL,8,F"they had received the best treatment
OL,9,Favailable" and therefore that
OL,10,Fcompensation was not required, the
OL,11,Freport found.
OL,13,FOn top of this, they failed to deliver
OL,14,Fa meaningful apology
OL,16,FA formal response by Government is
OL,17,Fexpected to be limited on Monday as
OL,18,Fcampaign groups have called for it to
OL,19,Fbe be a day for the victims and
OL,20,Ffamilies.
