OL,3,CInfected blood inquiry: What were the
OL,4,Cmissed opportunities?
OL,6,FBut it is expected that billions in
OL,7,Fcompensation could be made available
OL,8,Fto victims, and that Rishi Sunak will
OL,9,Fmake an official apology to all
OL,10,Fvictims on behalf of the Government.
OL,12,FThe report said: "A full apology from
OL,13,Fgovernment is to be expected, but for
OL,14,Fthat apology to be meaningful, it must
OL,15,Fbe accompanied by action.
