OL,7,Fthis treatment disaster and
OL,8,Fcompensation without further delay, as
OL,9,Fwell as implementation of the
OL,10,FInquiry's recommendations for a change
OL,11,Fof culture and practice in the NHS and
OL,12,Fthe Civil Service."
